{"id": 2249, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得在学习历史的过程中有哪些值得警惕的地方?", "description": "一说到屈原就是爱国投江、李鸿章是丧权辱国、和珅虽然坏但坏得有点可爱，历史这个任人打扮的小姑娘在我们眼里究竟应该是个怎样的形象？（题图来自：istock)", "record_count": 22330, "comment_count": 79, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180328142350twTVMBohDSxGQvE6.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-29T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3920, "title": "你觉得在学习历史的过程中有哪些值得警惕的地方?", "content": "你觉得在学习历史的过程中有哪些值得警惕的地方？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 273186, "content": "给历史人物贴标签，不是精忠报国就是卖国求荣", "image": "img/option/option/2018032815111591dBMoWeu0QgOFat.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 273187, "content": "历史教科书把有争议没定调的时间当事实写", "image": "img/option/option/20180328151245ckg7BmXSWFM6qnb8.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 273188, "content": "忽略历史书写者的立场，编写前代史书的总是当代人", "image": "img/option/option/20180328151423lJ0YDQhNucmbBdAV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 273189, "content": "老一辈人口述的未经验证的亲身经历，容易照单全收", "image": "img/option/option/20180328152053tncDVHuQl53gxhoF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 273190, "content": "认为历史是确定的，历史知识也不能被推翻和纠正", "image": "img/option/option/20180328152541KQniT4d7A3uMSCqr.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 273195, "content": "事后诸葛亮，站在决定论立场上看历史都是必然的", "image": "img/option/option/20180328153850YD3KGngClVTJodXH.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 273199, "content": "把古籍的史料记载等同于史实", "image": "img/option/option/20180328155033jxiwfJ405I9zAqN3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 273205, "content": "忽略历史的政治滤镜，把有选择的记录当历史的全部", "image": "img/option/option/20180328160224O5RAdxsZDz3ykpXq.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 273384, "content": "春秋笔法，同样的事用不一样的取舍编排就变味了", "image": "img/option/option/201803291544056j9fsQpZYPcJotwx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}